Major Findings
1. Save Architecture Was Not The Primary Problem

Initial symptoms:

Duplicate key errors on save
Stale current_dish_id
FK errors in child saves
Page appearing partially cleared

Investigation confirmed:

addDshItem was successfully inserting records.
Returned Dish IDs were being generated correctly.
Duplicate errors occurred because rows already existed.

Root issue:

Appsmith page state became detached from the saved Dish.

The page sometimes returned to:

current_dish_id = 0

while still visually displaying Dish data.

2. Dish Header Save/Reload Stabilized

Verified:

New Dish save inserts correctly.
